core":0,"quote":{"pid":"7207576d889f7316c79f3b3605cd6b96394bee4f","tid":2406246,"uid":130901,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"可惜，東德不是香港，蘇聯更不是中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:52:27.000Z","msg":"背景唔同但可以參考<br />\n走既原因都係個幾樣野<br />\n你係自己國家見到有將來有發展，有作為一個國家公民應有既權利，你點會放低哂所有野去到一個未知既環境街生活？"},{"pid":"9eb7157b5ee996004a6acc597bf4f022a172dffb","tid":2406246,"uid":37577,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"eed6f63cc56a87752c549ab13547a09b7e4f7eff","tid":2406246,"uid":378793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e830ae7c3656eee6857520ea0382b3a4f6cd331c","tid":2406246,"uid":28114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:29:51.000Z","msg":"召喚留港撚屌柒樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:31:04.000Z","msg":"我真係好撚鍾意呢個臭港 點都唔走架啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T09:55:07.000Z","msg":"根本走既唔走既都唔應該互屌<br />\n大家背景諗法唔同無得要人Follow 自己個套<br />\n唔走既自己諗方法點係呢個時勢繼續堅持做自己<br />\n走既諗方法點可以係異地生活落去"},{"pid":"4cbb15cad5df4452193ad23e4665782bfede2ba1","tid":2406246,"uid":353635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3bdbd693d41447b4876eb64891641be157ca5a3e","tid":2406246,"uid":2054,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T06:46:51.000Z","msg":"香港本來一個世界級城市<br />\n東西文化全世界絕無僅有<br />\n比中國搞撚到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T10:59:09.000Z","msg":"早幾日聽左沈旭暉講金閣寺同紫砂茶壺比喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"397a4f85102aaf340bb5028e30433e0cde9f20e7","tid":2406246,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7207576d889f7316c79f3b3605cd6b96394bee4f","tid":2406246,"uid":130901,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T05:17:44.000Z","msg":"可惜，東德不是香港，蘇聯更不是中共"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-13T13:30:25.000Z","msg":"蘇聯同中共都係差唔多咁殘暴,但都有一絲嘅人性,可能因為蘇聯人普遍教育程度高."}]}